 pass the level.\n2.Pay attention to avoiding monsters, monsters hitting lyme or the glass that lyme lights up will cause the challenge to fail.\n3.Guess the country by poster,have a fun!\n4.100% progress can get poster of this level (the poster will be placed in the Cover->Album). Repeating the challenge can increase the progress of the level. For example, the first pass opens the 50% area on the left side, and the second pass opens the 50% area on the right side to achieve 100% progress.", "short_description": "Control the cute elf(named lyme) to step on the closed area of \u200bthe glass to open the area. Open enough areas to pass the level.\nGuess the country by poster,have a fun!\n100% level progress can get poster of this level."}]}, "developer_name": "Zgame Studio", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.zgamevr.com/PrivacyPolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.zgamevr.com/TermsAndConditions.html", "publisher_name": "Zgame Studio", "support_website_url": "http://www.zgamevr.com/BuildingPanic.html", "website_url": "http://www.zgamevr.com/BuildingPanic.html", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PUZZLE", "ACTION", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1435841933480721"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982482_422890385151511_7945146459114962944_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=CDJluKj4hxIQ7kNvgG6VHQS&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.o